[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0046","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0055","title":"Sun Solaris chkperm 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 chkperm 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过传入超长的 `-n` 选项参数触发堆栈缓冲区溢出，从而在受影响系统上提升至 root 权限，实现对主机的完全控制。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统中的 chkperm 工具，攻击者需具备本地登录权限才能利用，利用成功后可直接获取系统最高权限，危害等级为高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0055"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:54.510","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Solaris 对应版本的补丁（如 Solaris 2.6 的 105484-05、Solaris 7 的 107014-01 等），并通过 `patchadd` 应用。如无法及时打补丁，可将 /usr/bin/chkperm 权限改为 0750 并移至 root 私有目录，或重命名该命令以消除本地提权途径，同时收紧 setuid/setgid 文件审计。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/918","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0055","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jpp8-gj33-w52q/GHSA-jpp8-gj33-w52q.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/918/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0055.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3f0ec3d0-95c4-4a6c-82ea-cedb1bef5a02.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0048","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0058","title":"Handspring Visor Network HotSync 未授权访问漏洞","description":"Handspring Visor 掌上电脑的 Network HotSync（网络同步）程序缺乏身份认证机制，远程攻击者无需任何凭据即可通过网络连接到目标设备的 HotSync 服务，直接窃取设备中存储的电子邮件、联系人、文件等敏感数据。该漏洞影响运行 Handspring Visor 的所有设备，由于同步过程中未实施任何访问控制或加密验证，任何处于同一网络可达范围内的攻击者均可利用此缺陷获取用户隐私信息，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0058"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:54.883","remediation":"Handspring Visor 已停产多年，无可用安全补丁。建议立即禁用 Network HotSync 功能，改用本地 USB 同步方式传输数据。若必须使用网络同步，请通过防火墙限制 HotSync 默认端口（TCP 14238/14239）的入站访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并确保设备处于受信任的内网环境中，切勿将其暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.security-express.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-01/0085.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/920","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0058.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0058","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0058.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/82035e540ee415f78310ba979a19dffd78d3cfa2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0058.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7m79-fmrv-9w39/GHSA-7m79-fmrv-9w39.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/920/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0058.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/pre2008/hotsync.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001087.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0111","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0057","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server CFCACHE 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 及 4.0.1 版本中的 CFCACHE 标签在处理页面缓存时，将临时缓存文件存放于 Web 文档根目录下，导致远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问这些缓存文件路径，获取包含数据库连接信息、文件路径、配置参数等敏感系统信息。该漏洞影响 ColdFusion Server 4.0/4.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，且无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0057"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:54.753","remediation":"升级至 ColdFusion 4.5 或更高版本以修复 CFCACHE 标签缓存文件泄露问题。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）配置中禁止访问 /CFCACHE/* 路径，或将缓存目录移至 Web 根目录之外。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=13978&Method=Full","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/917","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19712","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0057.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0057","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0057.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0057.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pf93-9cw9-mwx6/GHSA-pf93-9cw9-mwx6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0057.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.908","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0111.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0111.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0045","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0052","title":"RedHat/Mandrake/Turbolinux userhelper PAM 路径遍历本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat usermode 软件包中的 userhelper 程序存在路径遍历漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 PAM 认证过程中利用 `..`（点点）目录跳转技术绕过路径限制，导致获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Mandrake 6.x、RedHat 6.x、Turbolinux 3.5 b2/4.x/6.0.2 等多个 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0052"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:54.140","remediation":"升级 usermode 软件包至 1.11 或更高版本，该版本修复了 userhelper 对 PAM 配置路径的 .. 目录穿越检查。如无法升级，移除 userhelper 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/userhelper）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.l0pht.com/advisories/pam_advisory","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2000-001.html