面导航与权限校验机制，越权访问本不应由其角色可见或操作的其它 Webtop 功能模块与数据区域。该漏洞影响运行 Allaire Spectra 1.0 版本并启用 Webtop 管理界面的系统，攻击前提是攻击者必须已拥有任意一个有效的 Webtop 登录账户，利用方式即为登录后手工拼接或篡改 URL 以访问受限资源，属于权限提升类越权访问问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0050"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.890","remediation":"建议立即将 Allaire Spectra 升级至 1.01 或更高版本（其中包含针对 Webtop URL 越权访问的安全补丁）。若无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器或 Spectra 应用层配置基于角色的访问控制列表（ACL），对 Webtop 各功能模块的 URL 路径进行显式授权限制，仅允许具备对应权限的已认证用户访问；同时关闭不必要的 Webtop 模块、启用访问审计日志以监测异常 URL 访问行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=13976&Method=Full","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/915","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0050","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9f74-69gp-7hxr/GHSA-9f74-69gp-7hxr.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0050.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001078.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0042.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0042.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0041","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0049","title":"NullSoft Winamp 2.10 播放列表文件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NullSoft Winamp 2.10 播放器在处理 .pls 播放列表文件时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向受害者发送特制的包含超长条目的 .pls 文件，当用户使用 Winamp 打开该恶意文件时触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Winamp 2.10 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0049"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.757","remediation":"升级 Winamp 至 2.11 或更高版本，该漏洞在 2.11 中已修复。如无法升级，避免打开来源不明的 .pls 播放列表文件，并可在文件关联设置中取消 .pls 后缀与 Winamp 的自动关联作为临时缓解措施。当前最新 Winamp 5.x 版本不受此漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/12022","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/925","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19720","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0049.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0049","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0049.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0049.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6fm-rqxf-7hgj/GHSA-q6fm-rqxf-7hgj.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/925/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0049.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d554a8d2-2f56-47b0-89e0-1127877c6ad5.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0222","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0222.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0085","title":"微软 Hotmail HTML 邮件 IMG 标签 LOWSRC/DYNRC 参数跨站脚本漏洞","description":"微软 Hotmail 在渲染 HTML 邮件时对 IMG 标签的 LOWSRC、DYNSRC 等参数过滤不充分，攻击者可构造包含 JavaScript 代码的恶意 HTML 邮件，当受害者使用 Internet Explorer 打开邮件时脚本会在 Hotmail 域下执行。该跨站脚本漏洞可导致用户会话 cookie 被窃取、邮件被读取或转发，甚至以受害者身份执行操作。攻击条件为受害者使用 IE 浏览器查看包含特制 IMG 标签的 HTML 邮件，无需用户额外交互即可触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0085"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级至微软修复该过滤缺陷的 Hotmail 服务端版本；在邮件服务器端对 HTML 邮件的 IMG 标签 LOWSRC、DYNSRC 等参数进行 JavaScript 代码过滤，并部署邮件网关对入站邮件做内容安全检查，阻止包含脚本的 HTML 标签渲染；客户端在 IE 中禁用 HTML 邮件的脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0085","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0085.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f4j7-89mf-xg78/GHSA-f4j7-89mf-xg78.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0222.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0222.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0200","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0062","title":"Zope DTML 文档模板未授权操作权限绕过漏洞","description":"Z Object Publishing Environment (Zope) 的 DTML（文档模板标记语言）实现存在权限绕过漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可构造特制的 DTML 标签，调用受保护的方法执行未授权操作，包括读取或修改服务器上的敏感文件。该漏洞影响 Zope 2.1.1 及更早版本，攻击者仅需能访问 Zope 管理端口的网络连接即可发起攻击，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0062"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到 Zope 2.1.2 或更高版本；临时缓解可在 Zope 访问控制配置中限制 DTML 方法的调用权限，禁止匿名用户访问敏感 DTML 文档，并对管理端口设置网络访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/922","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000104222219.B41650%40schvin.net","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0062.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0168","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0059","title":"PHP 3.0 safe_mode 模式下 popen 函数绕过 EscapeShellCmd 过滤导致远程命令执行漏洞","description":"PHP 3.0 版本中启用了 safe_mode 安全模式，该模式本应通过 EscapeShellCmd() 函数过滤 shell 元字符来限制系统命令执行。然而 popen() 函数未正确调用 EscapeShellCmd() 过滤，导致攻击者可通过向 popen 传递包含 shell 元字符的恶意参数绕过 safe_mode 限制，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0059"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 PHP 至 3.0.14 或更高版本，该版本修复了 popen 函数未过滤 shell 元字符的问题。如无法升级，应避免在 PHP 应用中使用 popen 函数处理用户输入，并严格限制 Web 服务器运行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/911","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19708"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19708"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19708"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0068","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0082","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9104,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10786}}","description":"WebTV电子邮件客户端存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过精心构造的HTML邮件内容，诱导客户端在用户不知情的情况下自动发送电子邮件。该漏洞源于WebTV邮件客户端对HTML内容处理不当，攻击者无需用户交互即可触发未授权邮件发送行为，影响使用WebTV邮件客户端的用户。攻击者只需发送包含恶意HTML代码的邮件，即可在受害者不知情情况下利用其邮箱发送垃圾邮件或钓鱼邮件，CVSS评分5.0，危害等级中等。Microsoft已停止WebTV服务，受影响用户建议迁移至现代邮件客户端。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0082"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:57.770","remediation":"WebTV（后更名为 MSN TV）已于 2013 年 9 月 30 日停止服务，微软不再提供安全更新。建议立即停用 WebTV/MSN TV 并迁移至受支持的电子邮件客户端（如 Outlook、Thunderbird），同时在邮件客户端中禁用 HTML 邮件的自动脚本执行和远程内容加载功能，以防范未经用户确认即自动发送邮件的攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://net4tv.com/voice/story.cfm?StoryID=1823","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C33420%2C00.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0082.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0082","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0082.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0ea6b1a1298433599abdd2a4c6b6ce9f09476665/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0082.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8q32-cwc5-qxjf/GHSA-8q32-cwc5-qxjf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0082.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88223/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001074.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--aa180de2-5845-4d5e-9719-4ea087860ee0.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/39b9df25423a93bff6d75a66d90cb36757da74c2/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0064","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0064.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0078","title":"HP-UX aserver 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统自带的 aserver 程序存在权限提升漏洞。在 1999 年 6 月版本中，aserver 在执行时会调用 awk 命令，但其查找 awk 的路径来源于用户可控制的 PATH 环境变量，而非使用绝对路径。本地已登录的普通用户可通过在 PATH 环境变量中预先放置一个恶意的同名 awk 程序，诱导 aserver 以更高权限执行该伪造程序，从而实现本地权限提升，获取 root 等特权账户的控制权。该漏洞影响运行上述受影响版本 HP-UX 并安装了 aserver 组件的系统，攻击前提是攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，利用方式简单且无需远程网络访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0078"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:57.287","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 系统至包含安全补丁的发行版（如 HP-UX 11.x 或更高版本），并确保 aserver 程序使用预先设置的、包含完整路径的 PATH 环境变量（/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin），同时在 /etc/profile.d 目录中添加安全 PATH 配置，以防止通过 PATH 劫持获取 awk 命令的权限提升攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5728","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0078.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0078","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0078.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0078.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pc6-h4q8-hvmv/GHSA-9pc6-h4q8-hvmv.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0078.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001073.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0064.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0105","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0120","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10773,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"Allaire Spectra 1.0 远程访问服务模块中的 invoke.cfm 模板存在安全绕过漏洞。该模板在处理 bAuthenticated 认证参数时未进行严格校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造或篡改该参数值绕过身份验证机制，从而直接访问受限资源或执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Allaire Spectra 1.0 版本，攻击者可利用该漏洞在无需凭据的情况下获取系统访问权限，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。攻击条件为攻击者能够通过网络访问目标系统的远程访问服务接口，利用方式简单且无需交互，仅需发送包含篡改参数的 HTTP 请求即可实现认证绕过。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0120"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:02.523","remediation":"立即安装 Allaire Spectra 安全补丁（修复 invoke.cfm 模板中 bAuthenticated 参数可被客户端伪造绕过认证的问题），或升级至 Spectra 1.1 及以上版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 Web 服务器层面对 Remote Access Service 目录设置 IP 访问控制，仅允许可信内网地址访问 invoke.cfm 及相关管理模板，作为临时缓解措施。由于 Allaire Spectra 已被 Macromedia 收购且停止支持，长期建议迁移至受支持的替代平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/955","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4025","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0120.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0120","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0120.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0120.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7qr-7qxg-9c44/GHSA-h7qr-7qxg-9c44.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0120.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001071.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0056","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0069","title":"Veritas Solstice Backup 本地敏感文件恢复漏洞","description":"Solstice Backup（太阳微系统公司的备份软件）中的 recover 恢复程序存在本地安全漏洞。该程序在恢复文件时未对目标路径与文件权限进行充分校验，导致本地已登录的普通用户可以利用 recover 将原本无权访问的敏感文件（如其他用户或系统受保护文件）恢复到自己可读取的位置，从而越权获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 Solstice Backup 软件的本地系统，攻击条件为攻击者需在目标主机上拥有合法的本地账户并能够执行 recover 程序，利用方式即通过该程序恢复本不应被其访问的敏感文件。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0069"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.200","remediation":"建议升级 Solstice Backup 至 Sun 官方发布的最新修复版本（应用相应安全补丁）。同时收紧 recover 程序的文件权限，限制普通用户对 recover 的执行权限，并对备份数据启用严格的访问控制列表（ACL），确保仅授权管理员可恢复敏感文件，防止本地用户越权还原受保护数据。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0069","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0069.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0069","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/1694f40643791ff0eb87bac5ac75df888b7163d4/2000/CVE-2000-0069.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0069.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6jjp-38m8-v25v/GHSA-6jjp-38m8-v25v.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0069.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88225/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0022","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0011","title":"Ana